articles.title: Melbourne to ease world's longest COVID-19 lockdowns as vaccinations rise
articles.description:
MELBOURNE: Melbourne, which has spent more time under COVID-19 lockdowns than any other city in the world, is set to lift its stay-at-home orders this week, officials said on Sunday (Oct 17).
